{
    "key": 63854,
    "messages": [
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_ByronIntro",
            "en_US": [
                "Ah!\n",
                "That\u2019s Oreburgh\u2019s Gym Badge!\r",
                "I see, I see!\n",
                "You\u2019ve defeated my son.\r",
                "But that\u2019s no surprise.\n",
                "He still has much to learn.\r",
                "In place of my son Roark, I, Byron,\n",
                "will take your challenge!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_BeatByron",
            "en_US": [
                "You were strong enough to take down\n",
                "my prized team of Pok\u00e9mon.\r",
                "In recognition of that power,\n",
                "I give you this: the Mine Badge!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_ByronReceiveMineBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0} received\n",
                "the Mine Badge from Byron!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_ByronExplainMineBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Having the Mine Badge enables you to\n",
                "use the hidden move Strength anytime\f",
                "outside of battle.\r",
                "And you now have six Gym Badges.\r",
                "That means all Pok\u00e9mon up to Lv. 70\n",
                "will obey you without question.\r",
                "Here!\n",
                "Take this, too!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_ByronExplainTM91",
            "en_US": [
                "That {STRVAR_1 8, 0, 0} contains the move\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 6, 1, 0}.\r",
                "If it hits, it may also lower the\n",
                "target\u2019s Special Defense."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_ByronAfterBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Gwahahahaha!\n",
                "The Sinnoh region is vast!\r",
                "Tough Trainers like you and\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0} crop up constantly\f",
                "to challenge the old guard!\r",
                "With more young Trainers like my son\n",
                "and you two taking charge, the\f",
                "future of Pok\u00e9mon is bright!\r",
                "But I\u2019m not stepping aside just yet!\r",
                "I merely need to rededicate myself\n",
                "to training on Iron Island."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_GymGuideBeforeBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Hey, there!\n",
                "Champ-to-be!\r",
                "The Gym Leader here uses Steel-type\n",
                "Pok\u00e9mon.\r",
                "Steel-type Pok\u00e9mon have high Defense,\n",
                "so you\u2019d have to hit them hard!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_GymGuideAfterBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Oh! {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}!\n",
                "You\u2019ve beaten the Gym Leader!\r",
                "Good going!\n",
                "That makes it six Gym Badges!\r",
                "I tell you what, you\u2019re really turning\n",
                "into one fine Trainer.\r",
                "If you were to say you\u2019re going to\n",
                "try to become the Pok\u00e9mon Champ...\r",
                "No one\u2019d laugh at you now!\n",
                "I\u2019m in your corner, kiddo!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_GymStatueBeforeBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Canalave City Pok\u00e9mon Gym\n",
                "Leader: Byron\r",
                "Certified Trainers:\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "CanalaveGym_Text_GymStatueAfterBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Canalave City Pok\u00e9mon Gym\n",
                "Leader: Byron\r",
                "Certified Trainers:\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}\f",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "GymExit_Text_MustDefeatLeader_CanalaveGym",
            "en_US": [
                "You can\u2019t leave until you\n",
                "defeat the Gym Leader!\r"
            ]
        }
    ]
}